MORNING REPORT: COMING ATTRACTIONS 
The Rich and Famous: Entrepreneur Donald Trump will be in Los Angeles Jan. 14 
to emcee American Friends of Hebrew University's 20th annual Scopus Awards. The 
honoree for the evening: his business rival, entrepreneur Merv Griffin. The 
locale: The Beverly Hilton, which is owned by Griffin. . . . Incidentally, 
Donald and Ivana Trump, Barbara Walters and Kitty Carlisle are among the famous 
guests entertained by Harry and Leona Helmsley as "Hard Copy" reports on the 
lavish lifestyle of the Helmsleys at 7:30 tonight on KNBC-TV Channel 4. ALEENE 
MacMINN 
